comments: Vucevic (CHI) and Holiday (CHI) engage and disengage with one another as they establish position for a rebound.
Dosunmu (CHI) momentarily places his left hand to the front of LeVert (IND) before correcting during the drive, and marginal contact occurs.
DeRozan (CHI) jumps vertically and makes legal contact with the ball in LeVert's (IND) hands prior to incidental contact with his left arm on the driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) re-screens to legally establish himself in Washington Jr.'s (IND) path and absorbs the oncoming contact to his body.
Taylor (IND) momentarily ties up the ball in Vucevic's (CHI) hands as he legally spins for the shot attempt near the rim.
Dosunmu (CHI) momentarily put his right arm around Craig's (IND) front as he attempts to navigate around the screen, and marginal contact occurs.
Brown Jr. (CHI) slightly extends his left forearm into the front of Holiday (IND) as he attempts to cross the half-court line, and marginal contact occurs.

Brissett (IND) brushes Dosunmu's (CHI) face as he contests the driving shot attempt, and marginal contact occurs. Contact to an opponent?s head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
LeVert (IND) steps out-of-bounds along the sideline with his left foot as he begins his drive toward the basket.
Taylor (IND) commits a take foul on Thomas (CHI).

comments: Craig (IND) throws the ball out-of-bounds as he attempts to pass it to Washington Jr. (IND) during the in-bounds play.
